Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双语字幕制作及修订: 非傲慢即偏见@SubHD\N蓝光原盘只翻译了《梦中人》前半部分英文歌词\N后半部分并未翻译  故而未做双语处理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.23,0:01:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}每天你都有机会跟别人擦身而过{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}You brush past so many people every day.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.60,0:01:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}你也许对他一无所知{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Some you may never know anything about,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.57,0:01:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}不过也许有一天  他会变成一个朋友或者是知己{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}but others might become your friend someday.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.08,0:01:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我是一个警察  我的名字叫作何志武{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I'm a cop. My name is He Qiwu,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.15,0:01:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}编号223{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}and 223 is my badge number.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.08,0:01:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开\N{\rEng}Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.02,0:01:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住\N{\rEng}Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别挡路\N{\rEng}Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.09,0:02:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我们最接近的时侯  我跟她之间的距离只有0.01公分{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}That was the closest we ever got just 0.01 cm between us.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}57个小时之后{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Fifty-seven hours later,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.96,0:02:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我爱上了这个女人{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I fell in love with this woman.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  伯母  我是阿武\N{\rEng}Hello? Ma'am? This is Qiwu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.04,0:02:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是找阿May的\N{\rEng}No, I called to talk to you, not May.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.13,0:02:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是特地打电话来问候你的\N{\rEng}No, I called to talk to you, not May.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好吗?\N{\rEng}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我?  没事没事\N{\rEng}Oh, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她呢  是脾气大了一点  让她冷静一下\N{\rEng}Yes, best to let May cool down for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她想通了会打电话给我的\N{\rEng}I'm sure she'll call when she's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  伯母  你千万别跟她说我打过电话来  好不好?\N{\rEng}Please don't tell her I called, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  你要去看电影啊?  那我不打扰了\N{\rEng}You're going to a movie? I won't keep you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯父呢?\N{\rEng}Is your husband there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  伯父  我是阿武\N{\rEng}Sir? This is Qiwu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  不是  我不是找阿May的  我是特地打电话来问候你的\N{\rEng}No, don't call May. I just called to say hi to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的咳嗽好了没有?\N{\rEng}Is your cough better?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  你们赶时间啊?  那么我不打扰你们了  你们去啊  没关系\N{\rEng}You're rushing out? I won't keep you then. No, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  四姐在不在你这边啊?  不在啊?\N{\rEng}Is May's sister there? No?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三姐呢?  我想问候她\N{\rEng}How about her other sister? I just wanted to say hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}每一个人都有一个习惯  我的习惯呢{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}We all have our habits. Mine is to wait here{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}就是来这边等阿May下班{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}for May to get off work.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}阿May很喜欢来这边  因为那个老板说她很像山口百惠{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}The boss here says she looks like Yamaguchi Momoe. She likes that.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}最近我跟她分手了{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}She and I just broke up.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}因为她说我越来越不像三埔友和{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}She wished I were more like Tomokazu Miura myself.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,368复机\N{\rEng}Message for account 368?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密码  "爱你一万年"\N{\rEng}Password is "Love You for 10,000 Years."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿明找我?  阿May吧?\N{\rEng}Call Ming? You mean May?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拼给我听啊\N{\rEng}Spell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,M-I-N-G?  M-A-Y吧?\N{\rEng}M-I-N-G? It's not M-A-Y?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有听错啊你?  没有?\N{\rEng}Sure there's no mistake? You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂不懂英文?\N{\rEng}Don't you know English?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂?  阿明啊?  我知道我知道\N{\rEng}Ming? I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是阿May叫你打给我的吗?\N{\rEng}I guess May asked you to call.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  我没事  叫她不要担心  好不好?\N{\rEng}I'm fine. Tell her not to worry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会好好地照顾我自己的\N{\rEng}I'll take good care of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是如果她这么想念我的话呢?  你叫她自己打给我嘛\N{\rEng}But tell her she can call anytime she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用麻烦你  对不对?\N{\rEng}No reason to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?  她没叫你打给我?\N{\rEng}She didn't tell you to call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你找我什么事?\N{\rEng}Then why did you page me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去跑步?  你失恋了?\N{\rEng}You're jogging? Did you get dumped again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有?  那为什么去跑步呢?\N{\rEng}No? Then why go jogging?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛?  你神经啊\N{\rEng}A race? You've lost your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑步这么私人的事情  怎么可以随便跑给人家看?\N{\rEng}Jogging is private. You don't jog for an audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样  拜拜\N{\rEng}Forget it. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}每个人都有失恋的时候{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}We all get our hearts broken sometime.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}而每一次我失恋呢  我就会去跑步{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Whenever I do, I go jogging.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}因为跑步可以将你身体里面的水分蒸发掉{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}The body loses water when you jog,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}而让我不那么容易流泪{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}so I don't cry as easily.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我怎么可以流泪呢?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I can't be crying.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}在阿May的心里  我可是一个很酷的男人{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}May always thought I was a cool guy.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没和好啊?\N{\rEng}Still no go with your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都一个月了\N{\rEng}It's been a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再找一个吧\N{\rEng}Find someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿May吧  阿May不错的\N{\rEng}How about May here? She's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.53,0:05:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rEng}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她今天晚上早下班  你约她逛街吧\N{\rEng}She's off early tonight. Ask her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她暗恋你很久了\N{\rEng}She has a crush on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊  今天约了人家\N{\rEng}Can't. I have a date tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改天吧\N{\rEng}Some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你们真的愿意做吗?  - 是的\N{\rEng}- Are you sure you want to do it?  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把护照给我\N{\rEng}Give me your passports.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个\N{\rEng}Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个\N{\rEng}Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.23,0:06:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个\N{\rEng}Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  坐下\N{\rEng}Hey, You! You! Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个可以吗?\N{\rEng}Is this one okay, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 一个大的  一个普通的  - 0K\N{\rEng}- Get a bigger one, but nothing fancy. - OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  放下\N{\rEng}Hey, Put it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别拍了  放下\N{\rEng}I said don't shot, put it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别摸\N{\rEng}Don't touch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.27,0:07:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给大家啤酒\N{\rEng}Give them some beers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结帐\N{\rEng}Check, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}有时候我会在阿May家过夜{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Sometimes I'd spend the night at May's.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}可是为了不想让她爸爸妈妈知道呢{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}So her parents wouldn't find out,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}每次我走的时候  我都会从阳台爬下去{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I'd climb down from the balcony.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}也不知道以后会不会有这个机会呢?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Will I ever get to do that again?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 多少钱?  - 两千五百\N{\rEng}- How much? - $2,500.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后再说  好吗?\N{\rEng}Latter, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干嘛?  走\N{\rEng}What are you doing? Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个  过来\N{\rEng}Hey, you two, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟着我  去结账\N{\rEng}Follow me, go check it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也是\N{\rEng}These too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来\N{\rEng}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不在这里\N{\rEng}He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你知道他在哪里吗?  - 不知道  他说把这个交给你\N{\rEng}- Do you konw where he is? - No. He left this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}罐头上面的日子告诉我{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}The date on the can tells me,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我剩的时间不多{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I don't have much time left.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}如果我找不到那班印度人  我就会有麻烦{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}If I don't find those Indians, I'll be in deep trouble.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何穿雨衣?\N{\rEng}Why the raincoat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像快要下雨了\N{\rEng}I think it will rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}不知道什么时候开始  我变成一个很小心的人{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I don't know when I started being so cautious.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}每次穿雨衣  我都会戴太阳眼镜{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}If I put on a raincoat, I wear sunglasses too.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}你永远都不会知道什么时候会下雨  什么时候出太阳{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}You never know if it's going to rain or be sunny.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}368复机{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Messages for 368?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}请问你密码?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Password, please.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}"爱你一万年"{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}"Love You for 10,000 Years."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}有没有人找我?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Anyone page me?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}没有啊  整天没有人找你{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}No, no one's called for you all day.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:13:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}谢谢{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Okay. Thanks.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我们分手的那天是愚人节  所以我一直当她是开玩笑{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}We broke up on April Fool's Day, so I took it as a joke.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我愿意让她这个玩笑维持一个月{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I'm willing to humor her for a month.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}从分手的那一天开始{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Every day I buy{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我每天都买一罐5月1号到期的凤梨罐头{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}a can of pineapple with an expiration date of May 1,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}因为凤梨是阿May最爱吃的东西{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}because May loves pineapple,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}而5月1号是我的生日{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}and May 1 is my birthday.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我告诉我自己{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I tell myself{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}当我买满30罐的时侯  她如果还不回来{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}that if May hasn't come back by the time I've bought 30 cans,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}这一段感情就会过期{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}then our love will expire too.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  这个罐头明天就过期了\N{\rEng}Sir, this can expires tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边还有很多  你再换一罐吧\N{\rEng}Why don't you get another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\rEng}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天早上最早一班班机是几点?\N{\rEng}What time's your earliest flight tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要定位置\N{\rEng}I want to reserve a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人\N{\rEng}One person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你看过这几个人吗?  - 没有\N{\rEng}- Have you seen these people? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要看清楚  也有孩子\N{\rEng}Look carefully. They have kids with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的不知道\N{\rEng}I really don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你看过这些人吗?  - 没有\N{\rEng}- Have you seen these people? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.15,0:15:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这个人呢?  - 没有\N{\rEng}- And this? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有吗?\N{\rEng}No?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你真的不认识他吗?  - 不认识\N{\rEng}- You really don't know him? - No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见你跟他说过话\N{\rEng}I've seen you talking to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 爸爸  - 没事的\N{\rEng}- Papa! - It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.42,0:15:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的女儿呢?\N{\rEng}Where's my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂?\N{\rEng}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想怎么样?\N{\rEng}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你一个小时  如果没有什么消息\N{\rEng}If you don't have some news within an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你永远不会看到你的女儿\N{\rEng}you'll never see your daughter again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  给她冰淇淋\N{\rEng}An ice cream for her, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\rEng}Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}有的人为了钱  连子女都不要  但是他不像{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Some men might sacrifice their own kid for money, but he wasn't one of them. {\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}一个钟头之后  我就走了{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}One hour later, I left.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是警察  站住\N{\rEng}Police! Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我已经六个月都没有破过案{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}It's been six months since I nabbed anyone,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}可是今天呢  终于抓到一个通缉犯{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}but I finally caught a wanted man today.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}每一次我有好消息  我第一个想通知的就是我女朋友阿May{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Whenever I had good news, I always wanted May to be the first to know.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}喂?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Hello?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}喂?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Hello?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三埔友和  我要杀了你\N{\rEng}I'll kill you, Tomokazu Miura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:18:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  请问有没有5月1号到期的凤梨罐头?\N{\rEng}You have any pineapple that expires on May 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 今天几号了?  - 4月30啊\N{\rEng}- What's the date today? - April 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  明天过期的东西我们不会摆出来的\N{\rEng}That's right. Think I stock outdated goods?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有两个钟头  这么早就收掉了?\N{\rEng}There's still two hours to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:14.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过期的东西没人要的  人家要买也要买新鲜的\N{\rEng}Nobody wants stale goods. Get a fresh can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新鲜新鲜  什么新鲜啊?  就是你这种人  喜新厌旧\N{\rEng}With you people it's always "Out with the old, in with the new!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  弄一罐凤梨罐头  要花多少新鲜  你知道吗?\N{\rEng}You realize what goes into making a can of pineapple?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.23,0:18:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要种  又要摘  又要切  你说不要就不要啊?\N{\rEng}The fruit is grown, harvested, sliced -- and you just throw it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有想过罐头的感受?\N{\rEng}How do you think the pineapple feels?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  我只是职员  我负责卖东西的\N{\rEng}Buddy, I just work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫我去想罐头的感受?\N{\rEng}Who cares about the pineapple?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有想过我的感受?\N{\rEng}What about how I feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要抬  又要搬  还要负责扔\N{\rEng}I stock and restock this stuff all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也希望那些罐头永远不会过期  我还省功夫呢\N{\rEng}I wish it would never expire. It'd save me loads of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}你那么爱过期罐头是吗?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}You like expired canned food?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这里有一箱  全送给你  不收你钱\N{\rEng}Here you are. Take as much as you like. It's on the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}不知道从什么时候开始{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}When did everything start{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}在每个东西上面都有一个日子{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}having an expiration date?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:18:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}秋刀鱼会过期  肉酱也会过期{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Swordfish expires. Meat sauce expires.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}连保鲜纸都会过期{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Even plastic wrap expires.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我开始怀疑  在这个世界上  还有什么东西是不会过期的?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I'm starting to wonder: Is there anything in this world that doesn't?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师傅  秋刀鱼要不要?\N{\rEng}Buddy, how about some swordfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过期的  不要  你要吧\N{\rEng}It's expired. I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.48,0:19:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要?\N{\rEng}You don't want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.83,0:21:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}终于在一家便利商店  让我找到第30罐凤梨罐头{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I finally found my 30th can of pineapples in a convenience store.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}就在5月l号的早晨  我开始明白一件事情{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}As May 1 begins, I begin to understand.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}在阿May的心中{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}In May's eyes,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我跟这个凤梨罐头没有什么分别{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I'm no different from a can of pineapple.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.14,0:22:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃?  这么好的东西你都不吃\N{\rEng}You don't want any? It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.08,0:22:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}有人说  狗是人类最好的朋友{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}People say dogs are man's best friend.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.72,0:22:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}可是为什么在这个时候  它却不肯跟我分享我的痛苦呢?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}So how come mine won't share my grief now?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.98,0:23:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}不知道算不算是一个记录呢?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}This must be some kind of record.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.85,0:23:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}那一天晚上我吃掉所有的凤梨{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I ate all 30 cans that night.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.42,0:23:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}还好阿May不喜欢吃榴莲  要不然我一定是完蛋了{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Good thing for me that May wasn't into durian.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.02,0:23:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我好想去庆祝一下{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I feel like going out and celebrating.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.89,0:23:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}阿May可能已经睡着了{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}May's probably in bed by now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}可是我不知道另外一个阿May呢?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}But what about that other May?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.20,0:23:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  你回来干什么?\N{\rEng}What brings you back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.45,0:23:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天心情好  想看子夜场\N{\rEng}I'm thinking of going to a late movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.85,0:23:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿  她走了  她走了\N{\rEng}She's long gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.22,0:23:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了?\N{\rEng}Gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.75,0:23:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道等你啊?  女人不能等的\N{\rEng}You thought she'd wait around? Women can't afford to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.59,0:23:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越等越会晚  越晚越担心\N{\rEng}The longer they wait, the more nervous they get.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.73,0:23:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后担心得像发疯一样\N{\rEng}Drives them crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.83,0:23:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚跟路口那个Richard出去了\N{\rEng}She just left with Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.33,0:24:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有意思的话早点儿来嘛\N{\rEng}You gotta move quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.97,0:24:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}没想到在一夜之间{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I never dreamed{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.97,0:24:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我居然被两个叫阿May的女人抛弃{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}two Mays could dump me in one night.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.97,0:24:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}为了要平复我的创伤{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}To get over it, {\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.81,0:24:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我决定不再找叫阿May的女人{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I resolve never to go out with another May.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.88,0:24:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂?  Lulu啊?\N{\rEng}Hello? Lulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.81,0:24:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是阿武啊\N{\rEng}This is Qiwu.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.88,0:24:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来喝杯酒吧?\N{\rEng}Want to come out for a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.85,0:24:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡着了?\N{\rEng}You're in bed already?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.69,0:24:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么早啊?  这么早你能睡得着吗?\N{\rEng}How can you sleep this early?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.09,0:24:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡得着啊\N{\rEng}You were asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.82,0:24:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那没事了  拜拜\N{\rEng}Never mind. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.73,0:24:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  千子惠吗?\N{\rEng}Hello? Chieko san?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.40,0:24:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你猜我是谁?\N{\rEng}Guess who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.17,0:24:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  我是阿武啊\N{\rEng}Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.27,0:24:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来喝杯咖啡怎样?\N{\rEng}Want to come out for a coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.14,0:24:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?  你老公不答应  你什么时候结婚了?\N{\rEng}Your husband won't let you? When did you get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.55,0:24:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五年多?\N{\rEng}Five years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.45,0:24:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么我们五年多没见了吗?\N{\rEng}We haven't seen each other in over five years?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.48,0:24:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女儿都两个了\N{\rEng}You have two kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.02,0:24:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你开心就好\N{\rEng}You're happy. That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.52,0:25:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你幸福\N{\rEng}Well, all the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.06,0:25:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜\N{\rEng}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.17,0:25:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  请问江秀惠在不在?\N{\rEng}Is Kong Siu-Wai there?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.40,0:25:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是何志武\N{\rEng}This is He Qiwu.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.71,0:25:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小学四年级同班同学  坐你隔壁的那一个啊\N{\rEng}We went to fourth grade together.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.37,0:25:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你记不记得啊?\N{\rEng}You remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.82,0:25:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈  不记得啊?\N{\rEng}You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.52,0:25:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了  拜拜\N{\rEng}Doesn't matter. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.35,0:26:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}那30罐凤梨罐头吃得我的胃非常不舒服{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Those 30 cans of pineapple had left me feeling queasy,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.42,0:26:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}所以我去了一家酒吧{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}so I went to a bar.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.86,0:26:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}因为听说酒可以帮助消化{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I'd heard alcohol can settle the stomach.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.32,0:26:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧?\N{\rEng}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.62,0:26:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  没事  再给我一杯啊\N{\rEng}Fine. Another double.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.00,0:26:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}有一首歌叫作"日出时让恋爱终结"{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}There's a song called "Love Dies at Dawn."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.50,0:26:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我现在的心情就是这样{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}That's how I feel now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.17,0:26:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}怎么样才可以让我忘记阿May呢?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}What can I do to forget May?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.01,0:27:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我跟我自己说{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I tell myself,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.65,0:27:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}从这一分钟开始  第一个进来的女人  我就会喜欢她{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I'll fall in love with the first woman who walks in.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.19,0:27:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐  喝点什么?\N{\rEng}What can I get you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.89,0:27:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威士忌  谢谢\N{\rEng}Whiskey, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.87,0:27:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我有一个预感  她一定会喜欢我{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I have a feeling she'll like me,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.44,0:27:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}可是为了保障我自己  我要问她一个问题{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}but just to be safe, I decide to ask her a question.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.65,0:27:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐  请问你喜不喜欢吃菠萝?\N{\rEng}Excuse me, miss, do you like pineapple?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.89,0:27:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}噢  她可能不是本地人{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Maybe she's not Cantonese.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.79,0:27:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢菠萝吗?\N{\rEng}Tell me, do you like pineapple?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.52,0:27:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢菠萝吗?\N{\rEng}Do you like Pineapple?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.31,0:28:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐  请问你喜不喜欢吃凤梨?\N{\rEng}Do you like pineapple, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.35,0:28:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国语讲得还不错嘛\N{\rEng}Your Mandarin's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.52,0:28:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  我台湾来的嘛  你呢?\N{\rEng}I grew up in Taiwan. What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.68,0:28:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在不想说话\N{\rEng}I'm not in the mood to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.85,0:28:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你走开\N{\rEng}Please leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.02,0:28:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用说话没关系啊\N{\rEng}We don't have to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.96,0:28:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以坐在这边吗?\N{\rEng}Could I just sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.73,0:28:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里那么多位子  你干嘛一定要坐我旁边呢?\N{\rEng}There are lots of seats. Why do you have to sit next to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.07,0:28:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我看你  你很寂寞啊\N{\rEng}I can tell you're lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.00,0:28:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?\N{\rEng}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.47,0:28:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.07,0:28:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个女人  这么晚了还戴墨镜  只为了三个理由\N{\rEng}There are only three reasons a woman would wear shades this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.38,0:28:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一个呢  就说明她是个瞎子\N{\rEng}First, she's blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.91,0:28:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二个呢  就说明她在耍帅  所以要戴墨镜\N{\rEng}Second, she's a poseur.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.18,0:28:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三个呢  就因为她失恋\N{\rEng}Or third, she got jilted
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.02,0:28:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她不想让人家看出来她哭过\N{\rEng}and doesn't want people to see she's been crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.36,0:28:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你觉得我是属于哪一种呢?\N{\rEng}And which one am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.59,0:28:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失恋\N{\rEng}The jilted woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.83,0:28:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实没关系嘛\N{\rEng}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.36,0:29:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失恋很平常啊  何必哭成这样子呢?\N{\rEng}It happens all the time. Why cry about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.77,0:29:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失恋我也试过啊\N{\rEng}I've been there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.46,0:29:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  我失恋的时候呢  我就去跑\N{\rEng}I usually go jogging.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.37,0:29:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后跑跑跑  跑到满身大汗的\N{\rEng}I run until I work up a sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.81,0:29:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子呢  我就没有泪可以流了\N{\rEng}Then there's no water left for tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.68,0:29:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  你要不要试试看跑步?\N{\rEng}Wanna try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.11,0:29:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天已经跑了一个晚上了  我很疲倦\N{\rEng}I've been running around all night. I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.88,0:29:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想找人陪你聊天的话\N{\rEng}If you're looking to chat,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.92,0:29:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你找别人好吗?\N{\rEng}please find someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.39,0:29:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是想找人聊天的\N{\rEng}I don't particularly want to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.06,0:29:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想陪你\N{\rEng}I just want to keep you company.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.10,0:29:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我了解失恋的感觉\N{\rEng}I know how it feels to have your heart broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.97,0:29:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个女人失恋的时候  最需要就是一个肩膀\N{\rEng}A heartbroken woman needs a shoulder to lean on.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.87,0:29:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以把我当成是你男朋友也没有关系啊\N{\rEng}You can pretend I'm your boyfriend if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.54,0:29:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有男朋友\N{\rEng}I don't have a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.98,0:29:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没有女朋友啊\N{\rEng}And I don't have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.48,0:29:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今年几岁?\N{\rEng}How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.35,0:29:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊  我两个钟头之前呢  是24岁\N{\rEng}Two hours ago, I was still 24.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.51,0:29:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我现在已经25岁了\N{\rEng}Now I'm 25.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.26,0:30:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会喜欢你的\N{\rEng}I won't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.03,0:30:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说得这么肯定嘛\N{\rEng}Don't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.46,0:30:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好你再给我多一点时间  你就会喜欢我  对不对?\N{\rEng}Give me a chance. We might hit it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.37,0:30:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜不喜欢吃凤梨嘛?\N{\rEng}Do you like pineapple?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.97,0:30:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜不喜欢吃凤梨关你什么事?\N{\rEng}What business is that of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.40,0:30:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我想多了解你啊\N{\rEng}I'm just trying to learn more about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.78,0:30:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前交一个女朋友  我们在一起5年\N{\rEng}I was involved with a girl for five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.38,0:30:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是之后呢  她跟我分手\N{\rEng}But then she dumped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.32,0:30:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她说我根本就不了解她\N{\rEng}She said I didn't understand her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.29,0:30:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想多多了解你啊\N{\rEng}So I want to get to know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.76,0:30:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不会了解我的\N{\rEng}You'll never get to know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.36,0:30:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不让我了解你没有关系啊  可是你可以了解我啊  对不对?\N{\rEng}Fine. Then try to get to know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.60,0:30:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢什么样的男人?\N{\rEng}What kind of man do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.47,0:30:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}其实了解一个人并不代表什么{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Actually, really knowing someone doesn't mean anything.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.24,0:30:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}人是会变的{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}People change.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.45,0:30:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}今天他喜欢凤梨{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}A person may like pineapple today{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.45,0:30:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}明天他可以喜欢别的{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}and something else tomorrow.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.08,0:32:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  先生\N{\rEng}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.01,0:32:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打烊了\N{\rEng}We're closing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.65,0:32:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打烊了\N{\rEng}They're closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.06,0:32:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要去跑步啊?\N{\rEng}Wanna go jogging?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.09,0:32:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我想找个地方休息一下\N{\rEng}I just want somewhere to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.94,0:33:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我没有想到  她说的休息就是真正的休息{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}When she said "rest", I didn't think she actually meant it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.05,0:33:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}整个晚上  我看了两套粤语长片{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}That night, I watched two old movies on TV{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.12,0:33:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}吃了四次厨师沙拉{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}and had four chef's salads.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.77,0:34:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}当天差不多快亮的时候  我知道我该走了{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}When the sun rose, I knew I had to go.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.01,0:34:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}在我要走的时候  我帮她脱了鞋子{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}As I was leaving, I took off her shoes.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.84,0:34:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我记得我妈说过  如果女人穿高跟鞋睡觉{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}My mother used to say a woman's feet swell up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.08,0:34:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}第二天脚会肿{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}if she sleeps in high heels.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.86,0:35:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}她昨天晚上一定是走了很长的路{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}She must have walked a lot that night.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.93,0:35:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}像她这样漂亮的女人  高跟鞋应该是要很干净的才对{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Such a pretty woman should have clean shoes.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.11,0:36:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我是早上六点钟出生的{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I was actually born at 6:00 a. m.,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.34,0:36:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}还有两分钟我就25岁了{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}so I'll really be 25 two minutes from now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.32,0:36:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}换句话来讲{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}In other words,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.04,0:36:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我已经在这个世界上  经历了四分之一个世纪{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I've spent a quarter of a century on this planet!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.82,0:36:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}在这个历史性的时候  我去跑步了{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}To celebrate this historic moment, I go jogging.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.89,0:36:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我很成功地  让我身体里多余的水份蒸发掉{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I'll get rid of my body's excess water.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.10,0:36:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我觉得很开心{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}It feels good.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.97,0:36:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}要离开这个球场的时候  我留下了我的Call机{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}As I leave the track, I decide to ditch my pager.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.37,0:37:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}因为我知道今天没有人再会Call我{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I know very well no one's gonna call me today.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.16,0:37:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,368复机\N{\rEng}Account 368.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.60,0:37:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}请说出密码{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Password, please.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.90,0:37:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}"爱你一万年"{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}"Love You for 10,000 Years."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.43,0:38:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}你702号房间的朋友跟你说  "生日快乐"{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Your friend in room 702 says happy birthday.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.01,0:38:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.51,0:38:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}在1994年的5月1号{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}On May 1, 1994,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.41,0:38:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}有一个女人跟我讲了一声  "生日快乐"{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}a woman wishes me happy birthday.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.05,0:38:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}因为这一句话  我会一直记住这个女人{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Now I'll remember her all my life.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.06,0:38:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}如果记忆也是一个罐头的话  我希望这罐罐头不会过期{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}If memories ever come in a can, I hope that can never expires.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.29,0:38:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}如果一定要加一个日子的话  我希望它是一万年{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}If it has to have a shelf life, I hope it's 10,000 years.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.27,0:38:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我一支烟\N{\rEng}Give me a cigarette.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.04,0:39:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 下雨了  - 是吗?\N{\rEng}- It's raining. - Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.27,0:40:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[期限: 1994年5月1日]
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.03,0:40:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一杯可乐\N{\rEng}A Coke, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.76,0:40:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  你又去跑步了?\N{\rEng}Jogging again?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.67,0:40:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大男人一天到晚去跑步  这可不是办法\N{\rEng}Running around isn't gonna solve anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.24,0:40:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿菲呀  阿菲不错的\N{\rEng}Listen, Faye's not bad either.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.08,0:40:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁是阿菲啊?\N{\rEng}Who's Faye?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.08,0:40:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  老朋友才告诉你  她今天才上班\N{\rEng}Just started here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.92,0:41:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要就快点  要不然又便宜Richard了\N{\rEng}Make your move before Richard beats you to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.66,0:41:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 可是我不喜欢男人  - 男人?\N{\rEng}- I'm not into guys. - Guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.96,0:41:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让一让  让一让\N{\rEng}Coming through!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.43,0:41:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我跟她最接近的时候  我们之间的距离只有0.01公分{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}That was the closest we ever got just 0.01 cm between us.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.00,0:41:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我对她一无所知{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I knew nothing about her.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.87,0:41:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}六个钟头之后{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Six hours later,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.84,0:41:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}她喜欢上了另外一个男人{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}she fell in love with another man.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.53,0:41:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一份厨师沙拉  谢谢\N{\rEng}Chef's salad, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.10,0:41:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿走还是在这儿吃的?\N{\rEng}For here or to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.03,0:41:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿走的\N{\rEng}To go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.44,0:41:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你新来的?  没见过你啊\N{\rEng}You new here? I haven't seen you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.88,0:42:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢听这么吵的音乐啊?\N{\rEng}You like listening to loud music?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.15,0:42:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  吵一点挺好\N{\rEng}Yes. The louder the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.92,0:42:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用想那么多事啊\N{\rEng}Keeps me from thinking so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.26,0:42:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不喜欢想事情啊?\N{\rEng}You don't like to think?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.26,0:42:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你喜欢什么?\N{\rEng}What do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.03,0:42:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  想起来再告诉你\N{\rEng}I'll tell you when I find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.37,0:42:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢?\N{\rEng}And what do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.97,0:42:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厨师沙拉\N{\rEng}Chef's salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.00,0:43:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板  一份厨师沙拉\N{\rEng}A chef's salad, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.30,0:43:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是厨师沙拉?\N{\rEng}Chef's salad again?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.94,0:43:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天晚上吃不烦啊\N{\rEng}Aren't you tired of them yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.04,0:43:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 买给别人吃的  - 女朋友啊?\N{\rEng}- It's not for me. - Your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.21,0:43:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她爱吃厨师沙拉啊?\N{\rEng}Is that her favorite?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.41,0:43:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买惯了嘛  她也没说她不爱吃\N{\rEng}She never said it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.15,0:43:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是没说出来  你怎么知道她不想尝尝新东西呢?\N{\rEng}Maybe she'd like something different for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.52,0:43:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸鱼薯条  很好吃的\N{\rEng}Try fish and chips. It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.96,0:43:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一她不喜欢吃怎么办?\N{\rEng}What if she doesn't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.19,0:43:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你就买一份厨师沙拉  再买一份炸鱼薯条\N{\rEng}Get both and let her choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.56,0:43:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就得了\N{\rEng}You can't go wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.83,0:44:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 浪费钱  - 十几二十块嘛\N{\rEng}- Isn't that wasting money? - It's not that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.67,0:44:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她有个选择不好吗?\N{\rEng}It's good to give her a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.60,0:44:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊  一份厨师沙拉  一份炸鱼薯条\N{\rEng}Okay. One chef's salad, one fish and chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.07,0:44:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.15,0:44:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.89,0:45:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板  一份炸鱼薯条\N{\rEng}Fish and chips, please, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.69,0:45:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不对?\N{\rEng}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.40,0:45:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早说过她会爱吃  你不信?\N{\rEng}I told you she'd like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.73,0:45:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛\N{\rEng}You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.50,0:45:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不爱吃厨师沙拉也不说\N{\rEng}She never told me she didn't like chef's salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.17,0:45:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又...\N{\rEng}You never --
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.48,0:45:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又没有让她选择\N{\rEng}You never gave her a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.08,0:45:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有选择  她自然会说话啦\N{\rEng}If you had, she might have told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.35,0:45:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正换口味  今天晚上尝尝Pizza吧?\N{\rEng}Anyway, now you broke the routine. Try pizza tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.45,0:45:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Pizza?  不知道她喜不喜欢吃\N{\rEng}I don't know if she'd like pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.12,0:45:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是那一招  一份炸鱼薯条  一份Pizza\N{\rEng}Then do the same thing: Get both.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.76,0:45:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多花几十块嘛  别担心\N{\rEng}It won't break the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.53,0:45:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.04,0:45:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样?  今天晚上要不要尝点儿什么新的啊?\N{\rEng}Want to try something different again?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.74,0:45:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,热狗啊?  热狗不错啊\N{\rEng}The hot dogs are good.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.88,0:45:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了  给我一杯咖啡\N{\rEng}No, thanks. Just black coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.35,0:46:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?  你不买宵夜给女朋友吃了?\N{\rEng}Nothing for your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.19,0:46:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她走了\N{\rEng}She left.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.59,0:46:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊?\N{\rEng}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.26,0:46:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说想换换口味\N{\rEng}Said she wanted to try some new dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.09,0:46:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对\N{\rEng}I guess she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.03,0:46:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宵夜都那么多选择  何况男朋友\N{\rEng}Plenty of choice in men, just like food.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.77,0:46:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好的厨师沙拉嘛  换什么炸鱼薯条\N{\rEng}I guess I should've stuck with the chef's salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.34,0:46:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小事情\N{\rEng}It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.71,0:46:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不换换口味  又怎么知道你是真材实料\N{\rEng}She'll try someone else and see you're better.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.71,0:46:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早晚会回来找你的  你放心\N{\rEng}She'll come running back. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.05,0:46:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.57,0:46:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}每一架飞机上面  一定有一位空中小姐是你想泡的{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}On every flight, there's one stewardess you long to seduce.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.01,0:47:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}去年的这个时侯  我非常成功地{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}This time last year, at 25,000 feet,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.85,0:47:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}在两万五千尺的高空上泡了一位{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I actually seduced one.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.08,0:49:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我以为会跟她在一起很久{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I thought we'd stay together for the long haul,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.85,0:49:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}就像一架加满了油的飞机一样  可以飞得很远{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}flying like a jumbo jet on a full tank.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.62,0:49:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}谁知道飞机中途转站{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}But there was an unexpected change of course.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.47,0:50:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}给我一杯咖啡{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Black coffee, please.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.00,0:50:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}都一个星期了  她还没回来找你啊?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}A week and she's not back?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.07,0:50:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让一下\N{\rEng}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.34,0:50:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许她在外面真的有很多选择吧\N{\rEng}Maybe she does have lots of choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.11,0:50:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你不要等了  她选择她的\N{\rEng}Then put her out of your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.28,0:50:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也换换口味嘛\N{\rEng}You have plenty of choices too.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.55,0:50:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每晚都喝咖啡  可不行啊\N{\rEng}Black coffee every night's no good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.46,0:50:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说换就换\N{\rEng}Can't change just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.72,0:50:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢来好了\N{\rEng}Have to go slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.39,0:50:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  放心吧\N{\rEng}Don't worry. I'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.73,0:50:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事最好\N{\rEng}If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.94,0:51:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  是不是有个警察每天晚上来这里买厨师沙拉?\N{\rEng}Excuse me. The policeman who buys a chef's salad here every night ...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.47,0:51:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  你说663啊?\N{\rEng}You mean No. 663?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.31,0:51:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他今天休假了\N{\rEng}He's off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.61,0:51:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是星期六休假吗?\N{\rEng}Isn't he off on Saturdays?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.98,0:51:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换班了  他没告诉你吗?\N{\rEng}He changed shifts. Didn't he tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.96,0:51:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你看到他的话  麻烦你帮我交给他好不好?\N{\rEng}If you see him again, could you please give him this?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.67,0:51:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  没问题\N{\rEng}Sure, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.97,0:51:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.46,0:52:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.47,0:53:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[你的位置被取消]
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.11,0:53:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[把钥匙还给你]
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.26,0:53:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我有事出去一下  - 啊?\N{\rEng}- I have to step out. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.97,0:53:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我有事出去一下  - 噢\N{\rEng}- I have some things to take care of. - OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.76,0:53:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我有事出去一下  - 啊?\N{\rEng}- I have to step out. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.41,0:53:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 喂  你上哪儿去啊?  - 我也出去一下嘛\N{\rEng}- Where are you going? - I have to go out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.28,0:54:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨  今天晚上就你一个人看店啊?\N{\rEng}You here alone tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.15,0:54:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么就你一个人看店啊?\N{\rEng}You here alone tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.46,0:54:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才还都在这儿呢\N{\rEng}Everyone was here a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.00,0:54:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来  他们就全部出去了\N{\rEng}They ran off just as you walked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.97,0:54:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪里不对劲啊?\N{\rEng}Something wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.74,0:54:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啊\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.10,0:54:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 咖啡  - 谢谢\N{\rEng}Black coffee. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.98,0:54:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天晚上\N{\rEng}Last night ...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.75,0:54:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个女孩儿\N{\rEng}some girl --
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.95,0:54:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.99,0:54:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天晚上有个女孩\N{\rEng}Last night some girl --
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.69,0:55:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可不可以把收音机关小声一点啊?\N{\rEng}Can you turn that music down a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.17,0:55:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天晚上有个女孩  等了你很长时间\N{\rEng}A girl waited around a long time for you last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.11,0:55:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下一封信  说要交给你的\N{\rEng}She left a letter for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.71,0:55:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?\N{\rEng}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.75,0:55:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  是个空姐\N{\rEng}A stewardess.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.09,0:55:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 呐  你看看?  - 喝完咖啡再说\N{\rEng}- You wanna read it? - After my coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.76,0:56:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你还没拿信呢\N{\rEng}Hey, your letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.63,0:56:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放着吧  改天来拿\N{\rEng}Keep it for me. I'll get it next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.65,0:56:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  老板\N{\rEng}Hey, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.39,0:56:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么今天是你啊?\N{\rEng}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.09,0:56:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我呀\N{\rEng}I'm on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.19,0:56:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 663呢?  - 他请病假\N{\rEng}- Where's No. 663? - He's on leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.73,0:56:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请病假?\N{\rEng}On leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.19,0:56:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说被大头钉扎伤了  要留在家里养伤\N{\rEng}Said he got hurt by a pin. He's recuperating at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.60,0:56:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大头钉?  还有这种事?  真他妈逗\N{\rEng}Hurt by a pin? What's he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.57,0:56:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}她走了之后  家里很多东西都很伤心{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Ever since she left, everything in the apartment is sad.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.74,0:57:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}每天晚上  我都要安慰它们才能睡觉{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I have to comfort them all before I go to sleep.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.18,0:57:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}你知不知道你瘦了?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}You've lost a lot of weight, you know.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.05,0:57:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前你胖嘟嘟的\N{\rEng}You were so chubby before.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.85,0:57:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看你  现在都扁了\N{\rEng}Now look at yourself. You're so skinny.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.92,0:57:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何苦来的呢?  要对自己有信心才行\N{\rEng}Have more confidence in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.30,0:57:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你不要哭嘛  你要哭到什么时候啊?\N{\rEng}I told you to stop crying. How long are you going to cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.24,0:57:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做人要坚强一点嘛\N{\rEng}You have to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.14,0:57:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看看你  窝在这里像什么样子?\N{\rEng}You're so limp and shapeless. Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.44,0:57:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉  好好  我来帮你个忙\N{\rEng}I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.86,0:57:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是舒服多了?\N{\rEng}There. Isn't that more comfy?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.53,0:57:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么不说话?\N{\rEng}Why don't you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.90,0:57:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别生她的气了\N{\rEng}Don't be mad at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.00,0:57:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都有不清醒的时候\N{\rEng}We all have moments of doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.84,0:58:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给她个机会\N{\rEng}Give her a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.04,0:58:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不好?\N{\rEng}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.41,0:58:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}是不是很寂寞啊?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Feeling lonely?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.21,0:58:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}才几天嘛  用得着这样{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}You're a real mess.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.82,0:58:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}你冷啊?  我给你点温暖{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}You cold? I'll warm you up.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.93,0:58:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板\N{\rEng}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.93,0:58:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 吃饭了没有啊?  - 吃过了\N{\rEng}- How are you? - I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.33,0:58:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东西在那边  要不要帮忙啊?\N{\rEng}It's all ready. Need any help?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.60,0:58:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨  这点东西  不用了\N{\rEng}It's not much. I'll manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.54,0:58:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让一下  让一下  对不起\N{\rEng}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.34,0:58:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让一下  让一下  对不起  让一下  让一下\N{\rEng}Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.91,0:58:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 哎  是你啊  - 喂\N{\rEng}- Oh, it's you. - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.95,0:58:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好了?\N{\rEng}Are you better?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.18,0:58:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么好了?\N{\rEng}Better?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.42,0:58:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是说你被大头钉扎伤了啊\N{\rEng}He said you got hurt by a pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.16,0:58:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听他瞎掰\N{\rEng}Don't listen to his nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.93,0:58:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么最近老没见你啊?\N{\rEng}You haven't been around much lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.03,0:59:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换早班了  现在巡这一区\N{\rEng}I changed shifts. I'm on this beat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.43,0:59:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛?\N{\rEng}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.73,0:59:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 要不要我帮忙啊?  - 行啊\N{\rEng}- Want some help? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.57,0:59:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了\N{\rEng}See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.28,0:59:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  真够重的\N{\rEng}It's so heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.91,0:59:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算轻的了\N{\rEng}It's light today.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.72,0:59:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的工作蛮辛苦的嘛\N{\rEng}Your job must be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.35,0:59:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打工就这么辛苦呗\N{\rEng}Work's never fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.56,0:59:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会做这份工?\N{\rEng}Why'd you take this job?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.49,0:59:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我表哥请不着人\N{\rEng}My cousin couldn't find anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.16,0:59:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来帮忙  就暂时帮他了\N{\rEng}I'm just helping out for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.36,0:59:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你以前做什么?\N{\rEng}What did you do before?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.80,0:59:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做过的事可多了\N{\rEng}Lots of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.14,0:59:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我存钱呢\N{\rEng}I'm saving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.94,0:59:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,读书啊?\N{\rEng}To go to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.11,0:59:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想过\N{\rEng}Never thought of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.24,0:59:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是想玩\N{\rEng}I just want to enjoy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.75,0:59:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算去哪里玩?\N{\rEng}How? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.31,0:59:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便呀\N{\rEng}Anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.22,0:59:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加州\N{\rEng}Maybe California.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.82,0:59:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加州?  加州好玩吗?\N{\rEng}California? Is it fun there?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.02,1:00:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  不好玩就到别的地方去\N{\rEng}I said maybe. If it's not, I can move on.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.06,1:00:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢到处去玩啊?\N{\rEng}You like to travel?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.13,1:00:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不喜欢啊?\N{\rEng}Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.70,1:00:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无所谓  去也行  不去也行\N{\rEng}I can take it or leave it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.91,1:00:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那咱们约着一起去吧  我的钱就快存够了\N{\rEng}You can come with me. I almost have enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.98,1:00:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改天再说吧\N{\rEng}We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.72,1:00:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这人怎么老这样啊?\N{\rEng}Are you always like this?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.72,1:00:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那封信你到现在也没拿\N{\rEng}You never came to get that letter.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.72,1:00:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没空嘛\N{\rEng}I've been busy.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.39,1:00:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吧  你把你的地址告诉我  我寄给你\N{\rEng}Give me your address. I'll mail it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.46,1:00:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免得丢了\N{\rEng}Otherwise it'll get lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.33,1:00:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.23,1:01:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个地址?  咦?  你家挺近的啊?\N{\rEng}You live close by.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.59,1:01:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀  就在前面有空上来坐啊\N{\rEng}Yeah, right down there. Drop by sometime.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.40,1:01:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好呗  行啊  行啊\N{\rEng}I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.47,1:01:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  继续吧\N{\rEng}Well, let's keep going.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.44,1:01:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  你出了那么多汗\N{\rEng}You're really sweating.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.97,1:01:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还行吗?\N{\rEng}Sure you can manage?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.38,1:01:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行  没问题\N{\rEng}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.17,1:02:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}拜托  你不要老做白日梦了{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Stop daydreaming, will you?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.27,1:02:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}你以为你会唱两句就是歌星吗?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Think you're a rock star?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.57,1:02:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作不做  老是拿着红萝卜当麦克风\N{\rEng}You've been fooling around with that all day.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.68,1:02:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是人家要来吃的\N{\rEng}Who'd wanna eat it now?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.91,1:02:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要拿  拿卷卫生纸去\N{\rEng}Use a toilet roll or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.82,1:02:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呀你呀\N{\rEng}You too!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.29,1:02:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我没做梦啊\N{\rEng}I'm not daydreaming.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.26,1:02:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对  你没做梦  你这是在梦游\N{\rEng}That's right. You're sleepwalking!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.26,1:02:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  梦游  梦游呗\N{\rEng}That's right. I'm sleepwalking.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.30,1:02:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就梦游吧\N{\rEng}Whatever you say.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.40,1:03:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游吧\N{\rEng}I'm sleepwalking.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.04,1:03:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}那天下午我做了个梦{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I had a dream that afternoon.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.44,1:03:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我好像是上他家去了{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}It seemed I was in his apartment{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.75,1:03:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}离开的时候  我以为我会醒过来{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}and that I'd wake up when I left.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.25,1:03:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}谁知道  有的梦是怎么样都不会醒的{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I didn't know you never wake up from some dreams.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.29,1:03:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}有时候  我会回家吃饭{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Some days I go home for lunch,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.70,1:03:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}因为每一次回来我都可以有一个希望{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}because there's always a chance ...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.53,1:03:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你回来了\N{\rEng}I know you're in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.80,1:03:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快点出来啊\N{\rEng}Come on out.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.81,1:03:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我数三下\N{\rEng}I'll count to three.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.78,1:03:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一\N{\rEng}One ...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.85,1:03:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二\N{\rEng}two ...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.31,1:03:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三\N{\rEng}three!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.05,1:03:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}她以前很喜欢从衣柜里跳出来吓我{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}She used to jump out and scare me,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.02,1:03:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}可是最近少多了{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}but she hasn't done it much recently.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.65,1:03:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}哼  说的也是  玩得多也会厌啊{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I guess games get old after a while.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.80,1:04:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}那她会不会藏在厕所呢?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Maybe she's hiding in the bathroom.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.56,1:05:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂\N{\rEng}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.53,1:05:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂\N{\rEng}Hello!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.05,1:05:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜\N{\rEng}Dummy.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.52,1:05:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你的叉烧饭  - 谢谢\N{\rEng}- Roast pork and rice. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.49,1:05:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让一下  让一下  让...\N{\rEng}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.13,1:05:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\rEng}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.73,1:05:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 又在这吃饭啊?  - 是啊\N{\rEng}- Eating here again, huh? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.37,1:05:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还没吃完了吗?\N{\rEng}Will you be here a while?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.91,1:05:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事啊?\N{\rEng}Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.61,1:05:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?  没事  没什么\N{\rEng}No reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.91,1:06:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪里呀?\N{\rEng}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.72,1:06:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘了拿点东西  得回去拿一下\N{\rEng}I forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.25,1:06:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  对了  你那封信我还没寄呢\N{\rEng}Oh, I still haven't mailed your letter.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.79,1:06:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  有空再寄吧\N{\rEng}No hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.56,1:06:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系啊?  那等我有空再说吧\N{\rEng}All right. I'll get around to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.97,1:06:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么又搬回来了?\N{\rEng}Why are you back?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.24,1:06:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得赶交电费  先放这一会儿\N{\rEng}I have to pay the electricity bill. Can I leave this here?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.31,1:06:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  表哥啊?\N{\rEng}Hello? Cousin?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.08,1:06:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在还在菜市场了\N{\rEng}I'm still at the market.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.75,1:06:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  我这下大雨\N{\rEng}It's pouring rain here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.36,1:06:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特大  你听听\N{\rEng}It's pouring. Listen.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.69,1:06:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的?  我们这里出大太阳呢\N{\rEng}What are you talking about? It's sunny over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.30,1:06:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地区性雷阵雨吧\N{\rEng}Really? Must be a local shower.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.03,1:06:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  雨停了  我就马上回来了\N{\rEng}I'll be back when it stops.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.13,1:06:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住把电费交了\N{\rEng}Don't forget the electricity bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.77,1:06:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  知道了\N{\rEng}I won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.28,1:08:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了\N{\rEng}I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.85,1:08:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  行了  知道了\N{\rEng}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.91,1:08:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再来看你们  拜拜\N{\rEng}I'll be back to see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.54,1:08:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜\N{\rEng}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.67,1:09:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你吃的\N{\rEng}These are for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.51,1:09:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛买那么多荔枝啊?\N{\rEng}Why all the lychees?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.28,1:09:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我串门去\N{\rEng}They're for a friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.09,1:09:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}你跑哪儿去了?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Where are you?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.86,1:09:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是交电费嘛\N{\rEng}Paying the electricity bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.93,1:09:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}要交这么久啊?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}All this time?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.83,1:09:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呀  人特多  挤都挤不过去\N{\rEng}It's packed here. I can hardly get in the store.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.30,1:09:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看且得交呢\N{\rEng}I have to wait in line.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.97,1:09:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能每天都那么多人呐?  你交了好几天了\N{\rEng}How come it's always so crowded? You've been trying for days.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.14,1:09:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没办法啊\N{\rEng}I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.38,1:09:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量吧  今天交不了  明天再来呗\N{\rEng}I'm doing my best. Should I try again tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.38,1:09:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要了  这家人太多  你换别的地方去\N{\rEng}Try another store.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.85,1:09:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换别的地方去?\N{\rEng}Another store?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.59,1:10:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我换了啊  我真的换了啊\N{\rEng}Okay. You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.20,1:10:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rEng}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.20,1:10:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨  你去逛公司啊?\N{\rEng}Been shopping?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.03,1:10:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  我在帮一个朋友装修嘛\N{\rEng}A friend is redecorating his place.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.77,1:10:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你很忙啊  - 对啊  我事特多\N{\rEng}- You sure are busy. - I certainly am.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.44,1:10:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还喝咖啡呢?  别喝那么多  伤身体\N{\rEng}Black coffee again. It's bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.51,1:10:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上睡不着多喝点水\N{\rEng}If you can't sleep at night, drink water.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.45,1:11:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}梦中人{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Man in my dreams{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.25,1:11:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}一分钟抱紧{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I hold you tight for a minute{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.95,1:11:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}接十分钟的吻{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}And kiss you for hours{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.53,1:11:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}陌生人{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Stranger{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.30,1:11:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}怎样走进内心{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}You stole into my heart{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.07,1:11:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}制造这次兴奋{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}And set it all awhirl{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.57,1:11:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我仿似跟你热恋过{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I've been in love with you before{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.44,1:11:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}和你未似现在这样近{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}But never felt so close to you as now{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.98,1:11:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}思想开始过份{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}My thoughts careen out of control{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.66,1:11:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}为何突然袭击我{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Why have you taken me by storm{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.66,1:11:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}来进入我闷透梦窝{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Bursting into my dreary dreams{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.20,1:11:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}激起一股震撼{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Sending shock waves in every direction{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.12,1:12:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}梦中人{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Man in my dreams{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.89,1:12:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}多么想变真{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I want you to be real{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.69,1:12:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我在心里不禁{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}My heart can no longer resist{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.27,1:12:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}梦中嫱{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Searching in my dreams{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.31,1:12:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}这分钟我在等{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}At this minute I'm waiting{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.71,1:12:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}你万分钟的吻{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}To kiss you for hours{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.48,1:13:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}喂  是我啊{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Hi, it's me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.02,1:13:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}班机回香港了  要不要把位子留给你啊?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}The plane's back in Hong Kong. Want to make a reservation?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.49,1:13:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我还是以前的那个电话  打给我吧  拜拜{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I'm at the same number. Call me. Bye-bye.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.54,1:14:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  你的头发多漂亮啊  留了一些日子了吧?\N{\rEng}Nice hair! Did it take long to grow?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.01,1:14:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关你什么事啊  神经病\N{\rEng}None of your business.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.68,1:14:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够骚的啊?\N{\rEng}Kind of a flirt, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.48,1:14:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rEng}I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.86,1:15:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?\N{\rEng}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.93,1:15:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  不  你跟她挺熟的?\N{\rEng}Have you known her long?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.46,1:15:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啊\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.20,1:15:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}有一天  我突然心血来潮  我有一个感觉  她好像回来了{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}One day I had this sudden feeling she was back.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.61,1:15:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}不知道是我忘了关水龙头{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Did I leave the faucet running,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.88,1:15:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}还是房子越来越有感情?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}or is the apartment getting more weepy?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.11,1:16:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我一直以为它是最坚强的{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I thought it would cope all right.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.55,1:16:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}没想到它会哭得最厉害{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I didn't expect it to weep this much.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.35,1:16:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}一个人哭  你只需要给他一包纸巾{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}When people cry, you just give them a tissue.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.06,1:16:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}可是一间房子哭  你可要多做很多功夫{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}But when an apartment cries, it's a lot of work to mop it up.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.35,1:16:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会在这儿啊?\N{\rEng}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.92,1:16:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这里是我的家  我当然在这里  - 你的家?\N{\rEng}- I live here. - You live here?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.35,1:16:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来这儿干什么?\N{\rEng}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.42,1:16:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事  我买金鱼呗\N{\rEng}I came to buy goldfish.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.42,1:16:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这里有金鱼卖吗?  - 没有啊\N{\rEng}- Someone around here sell goldfish? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.23,1:16:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那你说你来买金鱼?  - 对啊\N{\rEng}Then why come to buy goldfish? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.50,1:16:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是买金鱼还是卖金鱼的?\N{\rEng}You buying or selling?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.55,1:16:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀?  你说什么呢?  我就是买金鱼呗\N{\rEng}What? No -- I mean, I'm buying.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.03,1:16:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问什么呀  我不知道  你别吓唬我\N{\rEng}Stop it! I forget everything when I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.07,1:16:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怕什么?\N{\rEng}Why are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.44,1:16:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕你呗  我看见你就害怕\N{\rEng}I got scared when I saw you here.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.84,1:17:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走了\N{\rEng}I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.01,1:17:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说要走  还站在这儿  还不走?\N{\rEng}You said you were going. Well?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.62,1:17:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我动不了  我这腿能动我不早走了吗?\N{\rEng}I can't move my legs. I'd go if I could.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.82,1:17:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是抽筋了?\N{\rEng}You have a cramp?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.46,1:17:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道  我没抽过筋\N{\rEng}I don't know. It's never happened before.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.73,1:17:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是进来坐一会儿吧  来啊\N{\rEng}Maybe you should come in and sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.31,1:17:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}每一次她回来  我都会为她按摩小腿{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}When she'd return from a long flight, I'd massage her legs.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.28,1:17:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}因为做空姐真的很辛苦{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Being a stewardess is a tough job.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.28,1:17:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}女人的小腿是最性感的{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I've always found women's legs sexy.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.18,1:17:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}自从她走了之后  我很久没有接触过了{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}But I haven't touched any since she left.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.19,1:17:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 好一点没有?  - 好一点儿了\N{\rEng}- Better? - I guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.03,1:17:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我能走了吧?  - 再坐一会儿\N{\rEng}- Can I go now? - Stay a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.73,1:17:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你听首歌\N{\rEng}I'll put on some music.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.09,1:18:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢这首歌啊?\N{\rEng}You like this song too?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.36,1:18:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无所谓  我女朋友喜欢它\N{\rEng}Not really. My girlfriend liked it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.93,1:18:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定你女朋友喜欢这首歌?\N{\rEng}She really liked this song?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.57,1:18:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.55,1:18:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我知道他女朋友喜欢的不是这首歌{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I know it isn't true.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.15,1:18:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}因为这张唱片是我前几天梦游的时候留在这儿的{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}That's my CD. I left it here a few days ago.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.42,1:18:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我开始怀疑梦游是否会传染?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I'm starting to wonder: Can sleepwalking be contagious?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.83,1:18:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}可能因为刚才太紧张了吧{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I guess I've been too nervous.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.06,1:19:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}坐一坐就睡着了{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}After a while, I fell asleep.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.12,1:19:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}那天下午  那个女孩子在我家里睡着了{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}The girl fell asleep in my place that afternoon.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.16,1:19:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}本来我想叫她起床{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I thought about waking her up,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.83,1:19:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}不知道为什么我没有这么做{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}but for some reason I didn't.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.33,1:20:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  糟了\N{\rEng}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.80,1:20:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当心着火  小心啊\N{\rEng}Watch out for the flames.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.70,1:20:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心那些蜡烛啊\N{\rEng}Make sure those candles are secure.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.64,1:20:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真不明白你最近做什么?\N{\rEng}What's gotten into you lately?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.91,1:20:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电费也不交  好了吧  现在电也被人剪了\N{\rEng}Why didn't you pay the electricity bill?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.48,1:20:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你每天下午都去哪儿了?\N{\rEng}Where have you been going every day?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.82,1:20:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看病去了\N{\rEng}I went to see the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.85,1:20:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看医生?  我怎么没见你吃药啊?\N{\rEng}The doctor? I haven't seen you taking any medicine.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.26,1:20:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃了啊  你没看见嘛\N{\rEng}You just didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.23,1:20:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我没注意  那么医生说你什么时候会好呀?\N{\rEng}Did he say when you'd get better?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.60,1:20:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快了  就快好了\N{\rEng}Should be any day now.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.56,1:20:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你生日快乐\N{\rEng}Happy birthday to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.31,1:20:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神经病\N{\rEng}You're crazy!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.65,1:21:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}不知道是不是因为换季{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Maybe it's the change of season,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.66,1:21:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我觉得自己变了很多{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}but lately I've changed a lot.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.09,1:21:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我的观察力强了{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I've become more observant.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.50,1:21:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}开始注意一些我平常不会注意的事情{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I notice things I used to take for granted.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.07,1:21:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}怎么番茄青鱼有生鱼的味道?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Even the sardines taste different.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.86,1:22:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要自暴自弃嘛\N{\rEng}You mustn't let yourself go.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.20,1:22:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前阵子看你还好好的  怎么一下子胖这么多啊?\N{\rEng}You were fine before. Now you've suddenly put on weight.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.14,1:22:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她虽然不在  你还得见人啊\N{\rEng}She left, but you have to carry on.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.31,1:22:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再放纵自己了  减肥\N{\rEng}You can't go on indulging yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.74,1:22:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就想骂你了\N{\rEng}You know, I have to tell you:
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.45,1:22:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你变了  你知不知道?\N{\rEng}You've totally changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.12,1:22:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做人要有性格嘛\N{\rEng}You can't just change personality like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.02,1:22:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算她真的不回来  你也不要改变你自己啊\N{\rEng}Her walking out is no excuse.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.73,1:22:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好反省反省\N{\rEng}I want you to think about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.77,1:23:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}看着它哭的时候  我很开心{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}It was a relief when I saw it crying.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.87,1:23:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}因为它外表好像改变了{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}It may look different on the outside,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.84,1:23:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}可是它的本质没有变{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}but it's still true to itself.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.78,1:23:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}它依然是条感情丰富的毛巾{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}It's still a very emotional towel.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.84,1:23:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉不觉得我开朗了?\N{\rEng}Have you noticed I've perked up?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.75,1:23:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我突然觉得什么东西都好看多了\N{\rEng}Things are starting to look better.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.98,1:23:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我觉得你很笨\N{\rEng}You used to look sorta dumb,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.95,1:23:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在看起来蛮可爱的\N{\rEng}but now you're looking quite cute.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.16,1:23:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把自己弄得那么脏嘛\N{\rEng}But you mustn't let yourself get so dirty.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.99,1:23:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前白白的多好啊\N{\rEng}You used to be so clean and white.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.16,1:23:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在弄得黄黄的\N{\rEng}Now you've turned all yellow.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.77,1:23:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看你  还弄那么多疤\N{\rEng}Look at these scars.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.30,1:23:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟别人打架了?  啊?\N{\rEng}Have you been getting in fights?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.25,1:23:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么躲在这里啊?\N{\rEng}Why were you hiding in there?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.75,1:23:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知不知道我找你多久了?\N{\rEng}I've been looking all over for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.85,1:23:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你躲起来没有用啊\N{\rEng}What's the point of hiding?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.62,1:23:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要面对现实才行\N{\rEng}You have to face reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.06,1:24:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇噻  发霉了\N{\rEng}You're all moldy.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.36,1:24:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天吧\N{\rEng}Tell you what. I'm not busy tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.93,1:24:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我有空带你晒太阳\N{\rEng}I'll take you out for some sun.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.38,1:24:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会在我家里啊?\N{\rEng}What are you doing in my apartment?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.18,1:24:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你叫我有空到你家来坐的吗?\N{\rEng}You said to drop by!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.02,1:25:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快开门啊  不然我撞门了啊\N{\rEng}Open up or I'll break the door down!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.76,1:25:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  有人找你啊\N{\rEng}There's someone looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.59,1:25:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 找我?  - 是啊\N{\rEng}- Me? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.87,1:25:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你怎么会在这儿?  - 我来拿封信\N{\rEng}- What do you want? - I've come for my letter.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.27,1:25:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么信啊?  你问老板啊\N{\rEng}What letter? Ask the boss.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.27,1:25:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问我干嘛?  在你那儿嘛\N{\rEng}You were keeping it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.01,1:25:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板说在你那儿\N{\rEng}He said you had it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.91,1:25:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我这儿?\N{\rEng}I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.28,1:26:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我这儿吗?\N{\rEng}I have it?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.95,1:26:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了\N{\rEng}Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.46,1:26:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕丢了  我帮你收起来了  我没有看过啊\N{\rEng}I was afraid someone might take it. I didn't read it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.63,1:26:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你啊\N{\rEng}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.13,1:26:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天晚上有没有空?\N{\rEng}Are you free tomorrow night?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.80,1:26:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛问我明天晚上有没有空?\N{\rEng}Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.87,1:26:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 想约你出去  - 干嘛约我出去?\N{\rEng}- I want to ask you out. - On a date?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.34,1:26:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板说你明天晚上不用上班\N{\rEng}The boss says you're off tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.01,1:26:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不上班就得跟你出去啊?\N{\rEng}So I have to go on a date?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.85,1:26:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你考虑一下\N{\rEng}Think it over.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.88,1:26:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天晚上八点  在对面那家"加州"等你\N{\rEng}I'll meet you across the street at the California at 8:00.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.06,1:26:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这首歌不适合你听\N{\rEng}That music's not your style.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.79,1:26:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听这首\N{\rEng}Listen to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.47,1:27:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完了  完了\N{\rEng}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.48,1:27:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完了  完了  完了\N{\rEng}Damn it, damn it, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.18,1:27:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  663泡妞真有一套啊\N{\rEng}No. 663 is a smooth operator.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.59,1:27:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 老板  你要学学663  - 神经病\N{\rEng}- It's 663. - Whatever it is!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.36,1:27:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等\N{\rEng}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.16,1:27:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 加酱汁吗?  - 好的\N{\rEng}- Chilli sauce? - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.81,1:27:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我的可乐呢?  - 可乐  没有杯子啊\N{\rEng}- Where's my Coke? - I'm out of cups!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.46,1:27:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}那天下午我在家里大扫除{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I gave my place a thorough cleaning that afternoon.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.49,1:27:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我好像在清理跑道  准备第二架飞机降落{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}It was like clearing the runway for another plane to land.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.67,1:28:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}那天晚上我早就到了"加州"{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I got to the California really early that night.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.34,1:28:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}因为我不知道飞机会不会Delay{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I half expected a flight delay,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.67,1:28:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我换了十块钱零钱{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}so I got some loose change.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.29,1:28:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  麻烦你帮我换零钱\N{\rEng}Change, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.44,1:29:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}半个钟头后  我又换了十块钱零钱{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Half an hour later, I broke another $10 bill.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.68,1:29:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我开始有预感那班飞机已经Cancel了{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I started thinking maybe the flight was canceled.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.14,1:29:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不会来了\N{\rEng}She isn't coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.07,1:29:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫我把这封信交给你\N{\rEng}She asked me to give you this.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.21,1:29:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着那么失望\N{\rEng}Don't look so down.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.58,1:29:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泡不上她  可以泡别人嘛  对不对?\N{\rEng}She didn't work out, so try another girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.88,1:30:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿May明天又回来做了  泡阿May吧\N{\rEng}May's coming back tomorrow. Give her a try.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.19,1:30:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 她人呢?  - 她辞职了\N{\rEng}- Where is she? - She quit.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.39,1:30:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说去什么  加州什么的\N{\rEng}Said she was going to California.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.76,1:30:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了\N{\rEng}That's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.50,1:30:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.70,1:30:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我没看那封信{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I didn't read the letter.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.74,1:30:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}因为有些事情需要时间去接受{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Some things take time to sink in.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.88,1:30:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}老板走了之后{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}After the snack-bar manager left,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.51,1:30:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我开始跟啤酒瓶讲话{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I started talking to the beer bottles.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.48,1:30:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}你失望了?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Disappointed?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.85,1:30:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}不会啊{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Not really.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.09,1:30:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}回家睡觉吧  她不会来了{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Go home to bed. She's not coming.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.70,1:30:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}其实她不是没有来{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Actually, she wasn't a no-show that night.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.77,1:30:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}只是走错了地方{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}She just got the place wrong.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.67,1:30:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}那天晚上我们大家都在加州{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}We were in different Californias{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.34,1:30:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}只不过我们之间相差了15个钟头{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}15 hours apart.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.05,1:31:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}现在是她那边早上11点{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}It must be 11:00 a. m. over there now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.75,1:31:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}不知道今天晚上8点  她会不会记得约了我呢{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I wonder if she'll remember our 8:00 p. m. date here.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.26,1:31:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\rEng}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.20,1:31:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么巧啊\N{\rEng}What a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.74,1:31:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用值班啊?\N{\rEng}Not on duty tonight?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.78,1:31:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放假\N{\rEng}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.95,1:31:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好吗?\N{\rEng}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.88,1:31:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不错  你呢?\N{\rEng}Fine. And you?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.42,1:31:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好啊\N{\rEng}I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.22,1:31:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人?\N{\rEng}You alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.86,1:31:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  跟朋友\N{\rEng}No, I'm with a friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.86,1:31:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很配啊\N{\rEng}He's your type.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.33,1:31:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还有东西在我家里\N{\rEng}You still have stuff at my place.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.33,1:31:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有空上来拿吧\N{\rEng}Come get it sometime.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.30,1:31:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要了  帮我丢掉了吧\N{\rEng}That's all right. Just throw it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.91,1:32:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.35,1:32:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要走了\N{\rEng}I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.78,1:32:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是比较想看你穿制服\N{\rEng}I still think you look better in uniform.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.79,1:32:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是\N{\rEng}So do you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.70,1:32:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 拜  - 拜\N{\rEng}- Bye. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.36,1:32:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  你买了东西  还没给钱呐\N{\rEng}Hey, you didn't pay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.09,1:32:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帮我给吧\N{\rEng}You pay for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.69,1:32:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 多少钱?  谢谢  - 262元\N{\rEng}- How much is it? - $262
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.33,1:33:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.00,1:34:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}那天晚上我收到一张登机证  时间是一年以后{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}The letter turned out to be a boarding pass dated for one year later,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.77,1:34:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}至于地点我一直没有看清楚{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}but I couldn't make out the destination.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.93,1:34:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[经济位  663先生]
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.02,1:35:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}其实那天我去了{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I actually did show up that evening.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.79,1:35:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我知道八点的时候人多  我七点一刻就到了{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I knew it would get crowded, so I got there at 7:15.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.36,1:35:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}那天的雨特大{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}It was pouring outside.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.76,1:35:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}看着窗户外边  我看见了下雨的加州{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Watching through the window, I saw a rainy California.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.27,1:35:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我特想知道  另外一个加州是否阳光明媚?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I needed to know if the other California was warm and sunny.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.20,1:35:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}所以我给了自己一年的时间{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I decided to give myself one year.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.01,1:35:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}今天和那天一样那么大雨{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Tonight it's raining as hard as it was then.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.38,1:35:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}望着窗户外边儿{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}Looking out this window,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.45,1:35:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我只是想着一个人{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}there's just one person in my thoughts.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.35,1:35:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}不知道他到底打开那封信没有?{\i}\N{\rEng}{\i1}I wonder if he ever opened my letter.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.88,1:36:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会在这儿啊?\N{\rEng}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.92,1:36:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你怎么会在这儿?\N{\rEng}Hey! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.05,1:36:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么是你啊?\N{\rEng}Is that really you?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.92,1:36:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛?\N{\rEng}Yeah. What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.59,1:36:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装修啊\N{\rEng}Renovating.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.29,1:36:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装修?\N{\rEng}Renovating?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.79,1:36:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我表哥呢?\N{\rEng}Where's my cousin?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.40,1:36:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你表哥开卡拉OK了\N{\rEng}He opened a karaoke bar.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.47,1:36:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说想换换口味\N{\rEng}Said he needed a change.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.60,1:36:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以让给我了  他没告诉你吗?\N{\rEng}He let me take over here. Didn't he tell you?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.44,1:37:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啊  好久没见他了\N{\rEng}No, I haven't seen him.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.44,1:37:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你表哥真会做生意\N{\rEng}He's a shrewd businessman.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.85,1:37:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚开始介绍我买炸鱼薯条\N{\rEng}First he sells me fish and chips,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.48,1:37:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在连店都让给我了\N{\rEng}and then the whole shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.18,1:37:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.09,1:37:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  你表哥很会做生意\N{\rEng}I said your cousin is a shrewd businessman!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.23,1:37:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么时候喜欢听这么闹的音乐呀?\N{\rEng}Since when do you like this loud music?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.10,1:37:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花点时间  适应一下就行了\N{\rEng}With a little time, I get used to things.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.70,1:37:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你不是去加州了吗?  好不好玩?  - 啊?\N{\rEng}- Did you go to California? Was it fun? - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.88,1:37:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是去加州了吗?  好不好玩?\N{\rEng}Did you go to California? Was it fun?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.49,1:37:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加州\N{\rEng}California ...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.76,1:37:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那么回事  没什么特别的\N{\rEng}was okay. Nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.23,1:38:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你穿制服很好看\N{\rEng}You look good in uniform.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.70,1:38:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这身也不赖啊\N{\rEng}You look nice like that too.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.47,1:38:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃不吃东西?\N{\rEng}Want something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.47,1:38:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃了\N{\rEng}I better not.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.44,1:38:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明儿一早我还得飞呢\N{\rEng}I fly out real early tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.11,1:38:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候回来?\N{\rEng}When will you be back?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.58,1:38:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里过两天就开幕了\N{\rEng}My grand opening is in two days.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.99,1:38:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\rEng}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.99,1:38:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这次可能得飞挺久的\N{\rEng}This might be a long trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.33,1:38:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了外国写封信回来嘛?\N{\rEng}Write to me when you reach wherever it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.67,1:38:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写了你也不会看啊\N{\rEng}You probably wouldn't read it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.95,1:38:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  有个事想问你\N{\rEng}I have to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.52,1:38:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有人给你这样的登机证\N{\rEng}Would you let someone board
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.69,1:38:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会不会让他上飞机?\N{\rEng}with a boarding pass like this?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.63,1:39:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日子是今天  可惜弄湿了\N{\rEng}It's dated today, but it got blurred in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.27,1:39:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不知道去哪儿的  你知不知道?\N{\rEng}where it's taking me. Do you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.04,1:39:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\rEng}No ...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.18,1:39:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然给你换一张吧\N{\rEng}but I'll give you another one.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.31,1:39:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\rEng}Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.23,1:39:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想上哪儿啊?\N{\rEng}Where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.43,1:39:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便啊  你说去哪儿就去哪儿\N{\rEng}Doesn't matter. Wherever you want to take me.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.88,1:39:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rEng}Written and Directed by
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.48,1:39:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rEng}WONG KAR-WAI
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.59,1:40:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rEng}Starring
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.22,1:40:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rEng}BRIGITTE LIN
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.66,1:40:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rEng}TONY LEUNG
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.43,1:40:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rEng}FAYE WONG
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.13,1:40:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rEng}TAKESHI KANESHIRO

